MOTION AND PROCEDURAL RULINGS

2009-0863. State v. Omiecinski.

Cuyahoga App. No. 90510, 2009-Ohio-1066. On motion to accept Proposition of Law No. I and hold the cause for the decision in 2009-1997, State v. Hodge, Hamilton App. No. C-080968. Motion denied. Motion to strike motion to modify denied as moot.

O’Donnell, J., dissents.
